description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, President Trump brokers a ceasefire in the conflict between Iran and Israel. That ceasefire is immediately broken. We’ll give you the latest, and then we’ll try to refocus the conversation back on issues here at home. Also, a new study shows that AI is making us stupid. As if we needed any help in that regard. Plus, a news station celebrates pride month by having a drag queen deliver the weather report. And is New York City on the verge of electing a foreign Muslim socialist as mayor?
